In {\mysystem} the tasks concerning counts and instances are separately tackled and a natural question arises as to how counts and instances are spread across the snippets and whether they frequently coexist in the same document, like (``He wrote 73 songs, for example Let it Be, ...''). Frequent coexistence would be very beneficial for the approach, since it would allow focusing on identifying snippets that solve both sub-problems at once.